The paper is about improving recommendation systems by jointly modeling user ratings and tips. This falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The paper proposes a deep learning framework for generating abstractive tips, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and language generation (cs.AI). The framework also involves regression for predicting ratings, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and deep learning (cs.DL) sub-categories.
